headline: JinkoSolar Holding Stock Earns Relative Strength Rating Upgrade
summary: JinkoSolar Holding ADR shows rising price performance, earning an upgrade to its IBD Relative Strength Rating from 70 to 81.

headline: Trade, policy ‘headwinds’ push First Solar to boost US production
summary: The Arizona-based solar module manufacturer commissioned its newest facility in August and plans to add 3.7 GW in annual finishing capacity by next December.

headline: 1 Value Stock to Target This Week and 2 Facing Challenges
summary: Value investing has created more billionaires than any other strategy, like Warren Buffett, who built his fortune by purchasing wonderful businesses at reasonable prices. But these hidden gems are few and far between - many stocks that appear cheap often stay that way because they face structural issues.
